high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge to the left
Open the fridge, remove the apple in the middle and then close the fridge
Turn left and then move to the table straight ahead
Put the apple in the bowl behind the spatula
Turn to the small table just to the right
Pick up the knife from behind the lettuce
Turn to the table to the left
Cut the apple into slices
Put the knife into the bowl with the apple slices
Pick up the bowl with the apple and knife
Turn around and move to the fridge on the left
Open the fridge, place the bowl with the apple and knife inside, close the fridge door
anns.task_desc: Preparing an apple and putting it in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around then face the fridge to your left.
Open the fridge, take out the apple inside and close it.
Turn left and head to the white desk in front of you.
Place the apple in the bowl on the desk in front of you.
Turn right and face the small black table in front of you.
Take the knife from the black table in front of you.
Turn around and face the white table to your right.
Cut the apple in the bowl on the table in front of you.
Place the knife in the bowl on the table in front of you.
Take the bowl from the table in front of you.
Turn around and face the fridge to your left.
Place the bowl with the apple in the fridge and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put sliced apples in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, and then to the left to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, pick up the apple inside, and close the refrigerator.
Turn to the left and go straight to face the white table.
Place the apple inside of the bowl on the table.
Turn to the right to face the black shelf in the corner.
Pick up the knife from the black shelf.
Turn to the left to face the white table.
Cut the apple in the bowl.
Place the knife in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the knife and apple.
Turn around go straight then left to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the bowl inside, and close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place the bowl with the apple inside of the refrigerator.
